Package branch

Class ItemManagement

java.lang.Object
branch.ItemManagement
public class ItemManagement extends Object
  • This class allows for adding,removing and editing of any item within the Branch
  • This is to be differentiated from a customer editing their own cart items,this class interacts with the branch as a totality
